ur identity within 10 minutes, your acount will be permanetly deleted.</mark></p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>Google</p></div></div></div>','2023-06-07 07:42:37','2023-06-07 07:42:37'),(14,39,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Webinar Team</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>webinar@journalism-webinars.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Invitation to a webinar on how to improve your writing skills</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p><mark data-explanation=\"4\">Greetings</mark>,</p><p>You are cordially invited to join a free webinar on how to improve your writing skills and become a better journalist. This webinar is hosted by Bob Jones, a renowned journalist and author who has over 20 years of experience in the field. He will share his tips and tricks on how to write captivating headlines, engaging introductions, compelling arguments and powerful conclusions.</p><p>This webinar is a great opportunity for you to learn from an expert and enhance your career prospects. You will also get a chance to ask questions and interact with other journalists from around the world.</p><p>To register for this webinar, please click on this link and enter your name and email address: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://webinar-5297.com/writing-skills?ref=journalist.com\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">https://webinar-5297.com/writing-skills?ref=journalist.com</mark></a></p><p><mark data-explanation=\"3\">Hurry up, as there are only limited spots available.</mark> The webinar will take place on Tuesday, June 6th at 10:00 AM CET.</p><p>Don’t miss this chance to improve your writing skills and become a better journalist.</p><p>Best regards, </p><p>The Webinar Team&nbsp;</p></div><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>webinar-invitation.pdf</span></div></div>','2023-06-07 07:46:36','2023-06-07 07:46:36'),(15,40,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+1-654-991-7623</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>James Millbury</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hey, it\'s me, James from Reuters.</p></div><div data-position=\'1\' id=\'component-text-2\'><p>I\'m working on an exclusive story about the human rights situation in China and I need your help. I have some sources and documents that I want to share with you and get your feedback.</p></div><div data-position=\'2\' id=\'component-text-3\'><p>Can you join me on this video call app? It\'s called ZoomSecure and it\'s very safe and easy to use.<mark data-explanation=\"1\"> Just download it from this link and create an account with your email and password: </mark><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://zoomsecure.net/download/\"><mark data-explanation=\"1\">https://zoomsecure.net/download/</mark></a></p></div><div data-position=\'3\' id=\'component-text-4\'><p>Then add me as a contact using this email:<mark data-explanation=\"2\"> </mark><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:james_reuters_2023@gmail.com\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">james_reuters_2023@gmail.com</mark></a> . I\'ll be waiting for you online.</p></div></div></div>','2023-06-07 08:11:18','2023-06-07 08:11:18'),(16,41,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+1-202-555-4321</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Rachel Gobdu</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello, I have some important information about the corruption scandal in the government. I can\'t share it here, but <mark data-explanation=\"1\">you can access it through this secure link: </mark><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://tinyurl.com/leaks2023\"><mark data-explanation=\"1\">https://tinyurl.com/leaks2023</mark></a>. You will need to enter your email and password to verify your identity. <mark data-explanation=\"2\">Don\'t share this with anyone else.</mark></p></div></div></div>','2023-06-07 08:13:28','2023-06-07 08:13:28'),(17,42,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>James Carter</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>jamescarter@internationaljournalismaward.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Congratulations!!! You have won a journalism award!</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Greetings!!! You have been selected as one of the lucky winners of the prestigious International Journalism Award for your amazing work in investigative reporting. You are invited to attend the award ceremony in New York City on June 15th, where<mark data-explanation=\"1\"> you will receive a shiny trophy and a huge cash prize of $10,000</mark>. To claim your award, <mark data-explanation=\"3\">please fill out this form with your personal and banking details and send it back to us</mark> by June 10th. You will also need to pay a small processing fee of $500 to secure your spot.<mark data-explanation=\"2\"> This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity, so don’t miss it!!!</mark> We look forward to celebrating your achievement with you.</p></div><span  data-explanation=\'4\'  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>Cash-prize.exe</span></div></div>','2023-06-07 08:16:11','2023-06-07 08:16:11'),(18,43,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Jean-Pierre Dupont</span><span  data-explanation=\'3\'  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>jean-pierre.dupont@europa-official.net</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Breaking news: A leaked document reveals a major cover-up</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><blockquote><p>Hello,</p><p>I am a former EU official and I have<mark data-explanation=\"1\"> something very important to share with you that could be the biggest story of the year</mark>.</p><p>I have obtained a leaked document that reveals a major cover-up by the European Union. The document shows that the EU has been lying to the public about the true extent of the refugee crisis, the effectiveness of the border control and the origin of the terrorist attacks. The document also exposes a secret plan to impose a martial law and a mandatory vaccination program.</p><p>This document is explosive and it needs to be exposed to the world. I have uploaded it to a secure cloud storage service and I have encrypted it with a password. <mark data-explanation=\"2\">To access it, you need to go to this link: </mark><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://eu-leaked-document.com/download\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">https://eu-leaked-document.com/download</mark></a> and enter the password: EU2023</p><p>Please do not share this link or the password with anyone else. This is very sensitive information and it could put me in danger if it falls into the wrong hands.</p><p>I trust that you will use this document responsibly and report the truth to the public.</p><p>Yours sincerely,</p><p>Jean-Pierre Dupont</p></blockquote></div></div></div>','2023-06-07 08:23:58','2023-06-07 08:23:58'),(19,44,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>David Lee</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>davidlee@greenplanetdoc.org</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Invitation to the launch event of “Green Planet”, a new documentary series</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>I am writing to you as a producer of “Green Planet”, a new documentary series that explores the wonders and challenges of nature in the 21st century. The series features stunning footage of wildlife, landscapes, and human-nature interactions from around the world, as well as interviews with experts and activists who are working to protect and restore our planet.</p><p>I would like to invite you to the launch event of “Green Planet”, which will take place on August 15th, 2023, at 7 pm, at the National Geographic Museum in Washington, D.C. You will have the opportunity to watch the first episode of the series, meet some of the filmmakers and contributors, and enjoy refreshments and networking.</p><p>If you are interested in attending this event, please RSVP by August 1st, 2023, by filling out this form: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://forms.gle/6tQJ8Z9yFw8zLZnC9\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">https://forms.gle/6tQJ8Z9yFw8zLZnC9</mark></a></p><p>I look forward to seeing you at the launch event of “Green Planet”, a documentary series that will inspire and inform viewers about the beauty and urgency of our natural world.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>David Lee<br>Producer of “Green Planet”<br>https://greenplanetdoc.org</p></div></div></div>','2023-06-27 16:42:53','2023-06-27 16:42:53'),(21,46,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Maya Rodriguez</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>mayarodriguez@gmail.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Preserving Indigenous Languages: A Cultural Legacy at Risk</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>I hope this email finds you well. My name is Maya Rodriguez. I work to preserve and promote the cultural heritage of indigenous communities worldwide. I am writing to draw your attention to the rapid decline of indigenous languages.</p><p>Indigenous languages are not merely a means of communication; they are the backbone of cultural identity, ancestral wisdom, and traditional knowledge. However, globalization, urbanization, and cultural assimilation have led to a significant loss of indigenous languages, placing the cultural legacy of indigenous communities at risk.</p><p>In collaboration with indigenous organizations, I have launched the \"Language Revitalization Initiative,\" a grassroots movement aimed at raising awareness about the importance of preserving indigenous languages and supporting efforts to revitalize them. Our initiative focuses on community-driven projects, educational programs, and the integration of digital tools to ensure the transmission of these invaluable linguistic treasures to future generations.</p><p>If you are interested in learning more about the initiative or featuring it in an upcoming article, I would be honored to provide you with further information, personal insights, and stories of resilience from indigenous communities striving to preserve their languages.</p><p>Together, let us raise our voices and take a stand for the preservation of indigenous languages, ensuring the rich tapestry of human culture continues to thrive for generations to come. I eagerly await the opportunity to collaborate with you in this endeavor.</p><p>Warm regards,</p><p>Maya Rodriguez</p></div></div></div>','2023-06-28 19:02:48','2023-06-28 19:02:48'),(22,47,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+33755348290</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Conrad Skyler</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello {{name}}, my name is Tommy Lee, I am a journalist at Le Monde. We are launching a new investigation based on a large trove of documents that was recently leaked, and we are forming a consortium to collaboratively search the documents and publish findings. Would you be interested in joining? If so, we can get on a call so I can tell you more about it.</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-08 06:04:09','2023-07-08 06:04:09'),(23,48,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Ahmed Abdullah</span><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+972-287-89-311</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello, I just wanted to bring your attention to some of the events in our community in the past few weeks: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wes6zK8GE\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wes6zK8GE</a>. We need all the support and coverage we can get!</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-08 06:05:20','2023-07-08 06:05:20'),(24,49,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Bluesky</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>noreply@bsky.app</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>We\'ve updated our Terms of Service & Community Guidelines</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>We have updated our Terms of Service and Community Guidelines. Our goal was to incorporate feedback we\'ve received from the community to make both these documents clearer, more detailed, and easier to understand.</p><p>We encourage you to review the updated&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://t.mmtrkr.com/clicks/html/c04d266c-6093-5140-b4c3-9c628d04cebd/7c550497-8b68-5fd2-8bc2-62eb13b55071/247f24c0-bf7e-5943-845d-92b517dcd1ca?urlChildId=e0625e58-59ab-58dc-9ee4-55fa8f952714&amp;templateId=6fd23758-e315-4cf7-a0fc-dbf860f09925\">Terms of Service</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://t.mmtrkr.com/clicks