a Hernández</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello, I’m Luis, a student from the University of Guadalajara. I remember you from the conference and I loved your presentation on social movements. It was amazing how you explained how you analyzed the impact of digital media. How are you doing? Are you working on any new projects?</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 18:46:12','2023-07-14 18:46:12'),(34,60,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Park Min-jun</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>parkminjun@kaist.ac.kr</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Application for PhD position in your research group</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear Professor Lee,<br><br>I am writing to express my interest in applying for the PhD position in your research group. I have a master’s degree in Computer Science from KAIST, where I worked on natural language processing project under the supervision of Dr. Kim. My research interests include machine learning, sentiment analysis and text summarization, which align well with your current work on generating headlines from news articles.<br><br>I have attached my CV and a sample of my publications for your reference. I would appreciate it if you could review my application and let me know if I am a suitable candidate for the position. I am available for an interview at your convenience.<br><br>Thank you for your time and consideration.<br><br>Sincerely, <br><br>Park Min-jun <br>Master’s student in Computer Science <br>KAIST</p></div><span  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>ParkMinjun - CV.pdf</span><span  data-position=2 id=\'component-attachment-3\'>Sample publication.pdf</span></div></div>','2023-07-14 18:47:40','2023-07-14 18:47:40'),(35,61,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Zara Mwamba</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>zara.mwamba@lakevictoria.uni</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Invitation to speak at Lake Victoria University seminar series</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear Dr {{name}},</p><p>I am writing to invite you to give a guest lecture at our department seminar series. I am a faculty member in the Department of Psychology at Lake Victoria University, and I have been following your research on emotional intelligence with great interest. Your work on measuring and enhancing emotional intelligence in children is very innovative and relevant to our current topics of discussion.</p><p>The seminar series is held every month and attracts a diverse audience of students, researchers and practitioners from various fields. The format is a 45-minute presentation followed by a 15-minute Q&amp;A session. We can offer you an honorarium of $500 and cover your travel and accommodation expenses.</p><p>If you are interested in participating, please let me know your availability for the next semester. I look forward to hearing from you soon.</p><p>Best regards,</p><p>Zara Mwamba <br>Associate Professor of Psychology <br>Lake Victoria University</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 18:50:23','2023-07-14 18:50:23'),(36,62,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Joe Sternlieb</span><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>joe.sternlieb@georgetown-uni.net</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>[ACTION REQUIRED] Georgetown University Employee Survey from The CEO Joe Sternlieb</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Georgetown University Employees,</p><p>In an effort to get better insight regarding utilization and value of core marketing and platform tools, <mark data-explanation=\"2\">your feedback is highly Urgent</mark>.</p><p>Please complete the following new updated 45-second survey which is important All staffs access by Tuesday before 3:00 p.m   It will truly only take 30-45 seconds.</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://secureform.truwwu.fr\"><mark data-explanation=\"3\">CLICK HERE TO TAKE URGENT SURVEY</mark></a></p><p>Thank you for your hard work and continued dedication</p><p>Joe M. Sternlieb</p><p>Chief Executive Officer at   GEORGETOWN UNIVERSITY</p><p>-------------------------------</p><p><strong>A </strong>3300 Whitehaven Street NW, Suite 5000 Washington, D.C. District of Columbia 20007<br><strong>P </strong>(202) 298-9222 ext. 207<br><strong>W </strong><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://www.georgetown.edu\">www.georgetown.edu</a></p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 18:54:24','2023-07-14 18:54:24'),(37,63,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Fatima Al-Sayed</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>fatima@worldbroadcasting.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>UNICEF Job Opportunity</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>I am sharing a UNICEF Job opportunity to all students and employees who might be interested in a Part-Time job with a $500/weekly pay.</p><p>Attached is further information about the employment schedule. Kindly follow the steps in the attached document and contact Mr. Ramu with your alternate/non-official email address i.e Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail, etc.) For more details on the employment.</p><p>Take note; this is strictly a work-from-home position.</p><p>Sincerly,<br>Fatima</p><p>Our broadcast stations do not discriminate unlawfully in the sale of advertising time on the basis of race, ethnicity or other legally prohibited grounds, and they will not accept, enter into or fulfill any contract or order for the purchase of advertising time that discriminates unlawfully on such a basis. In placing advertising on one or more of our broadcast stations, advertisers confirm their compliance with this requirement<mark data-explanation=\"1\"> .&amp;&amp; </mark>Please only print if necessary.</p></div><span  data-explanation=\'2\'  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>application.pdf</span></div></div>','2023-07-14 18:56:39','2023-07-14 18:56:39'),(38,64,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Lisa Smith</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>lisa.smith@socialmediamarketing.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>New report on social media trends - your feedback wanted</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hi {{name}},</p><p>I hope this email finds you well and that you are enjoying your summer.</p><p>I’m writing to share with you a new report that I’ve been working on for the past few months. It’s called “Social Media Trends 2023: How to Stay Ahead of the Curve” and it covers the latest developments, challenges and opportunities in the social media landscape.</p><p>The report is based on extensive research, interviews and surveys with experts, influencers and consumers. It provides insights and recommendations on topics such as:</p><ul><li><p>The rise of short-form video and audio content</p></li><li><p>The impact of social commerce and live-streaming on consumer behavior</p></li><li><p>The best practices for engaging with niche communities and micro-influencers</p></li><li><p>The emerging platforms and features that you need to watch out for</p></li><li><p>The ethical and legal implications of social media marketing in 2023</p></li></ul><p>I think you will find this report very valuable and relevant for your work. I would love to hear your feedback and thoughts on it. You can download the report for free from this link: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.socialmediatrends2023.com/\">https://www.socialmediatrends2023.com/</a></p><p>Please let me know what you think and if you have any questions or suggestions. I look forward to hearing from you soon.</p><p>Best,</p><p>Jane</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:02:27','2023-07-14 19:02:27'),(39,65,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+27 12 345 6789</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Kwanele Mosi</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hi {{name}}, how are you? I hope you’re doing well. I have a great opportunity for you. I’ve been contacted by a potential client who is looking for a social media marketing consultant. They are a big brand in the fashion industry and they want to revamp their online presence. I think you would be perfect for this project. You can check out their website here: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.fashionbrand.com/\">https://www.fashionbrand.com/</a> Let me know if you want me to connect you with them!</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:03:17','2023-07-14 19:03:17'),(40,66,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+63 917 123 4567</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Sipatuan Bigay</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p><mark data-explanation=\"1\">Hello</mark>, as you may be aware, the healthcare authorities have issued new guidelines for healthcare workers regarding the COVID-19 vaccination. To ensure compliance with these guidelines, we require you to update your vaccination status in our online portal as soon as possible. <mark data-explanation=\"2\">Please click on this link and log in with your employee ID and password</mark> to access the portal and update your information.&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://vaccination-status-update.rz/portal/login\">https://vaccination-status-update.rz/portal/login</a>. <mark data-explanation=\"4\">If you do not update your vaccination status by next week, you may face disciplinary action or termination of employment</mark>. Thank you.</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:06:19','2023-07-14 19:06:19'),(41,67,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+998 90 123 4567</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Zara Khamidova</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello {{name}}, this is Dr. Zara Khamidova from the National Institute of Health. <mark data-explanation=\"3\">You have won a $10,000 research grant</mark>. Congrats! To claim it, fill out the attached form and email with your ID and CV. <mark data-explanation=\"2\">Hurry, you have 15 days to do it</mark>.</p></div><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>Grant winner form.pdf</span></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:09:08','2023-07-14 19:09:08'),(42,68,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Diego Sánchez</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>diego.s@ata.org</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Invitation to a webinar on telehealth best practices</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>We are pleased to invite you to a webinar on telehealth best practices, hosted by the American Telemedicine Association (ATA) on August 20, 2023 at 10:00 AM PST.</p><p>This webinar will feature experts from the field of telehealth who will share their insights and experiences on how to deliver high-quality, patient-centered care using digital technologies. You will also learn about the latest trends, challenges, and opportunities in telehealth, as well as the best practices for ensuring compliance, security, and privacy.</p><p>The webinar is free. To register, please visit this link: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://ata.org/webinar/telehealth-best-practices\">https://ata.org/webinar/telehealth-best-practices</a></p><p>We hope you can join us for this informative and interactive session. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:info@ata.org\">info@ata.org</a>.</p><p>Sincerely,<br>The ATA Team</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:10:18','2023-07-14 19:10:18'),(43,69,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Dr. Maria Garcia</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>mgarcia@medschool.edu</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Invitation to collaborate on a research project</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>I am writing to invite you to collaborate on a research project that I am leading at the Medical School of the University of Buenos Aires. The project aims to evaluate the impact of a novel intervention for chronic pain management in primary care settings.</p><p>The intervention is based on a multidisciplinary approach that combines pharmacological, psychological, and physical therapies, tailored to the individual needs and preferences of each patient. We have developed a protocol and a training program for the primary care providers who will deliver the intervention, and we are ready to start the recruitment and randomization of the participants.</p><p>We are looking for partners who can help us implement the intervention in their clinics, collect data, and disseminate the results. We believe that your expertise and experience in chronic pain management would be a valuable asset for our project, and we would greatly appreciate your involvement.</p><p>I hope to hear from you soon and to have the opportunity to work with you on this exciting and important project.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>Dr. Maria Garcia<br>Associate Professor of Family Medicine<br>Medical School of the University of Buenos Aires</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:11:42','2023-07-14 19:11:42'),(44,70,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+381 11 1234567</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Nikola Petrovic</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello, this is Dr. Lee from the radiology department. I just reviewed your patient’s MRI scan and I have some important findings to discuss with you. Please call me back as soon as possible.</p></div></div></div>','2023-07-14 19:12:36','2023-07-14 19:12:36'),(45,71,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Amnesty International</span><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>amnesty.international@intl-survey.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Amnesty International Survey</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>We are Amnesty International, a global movement of more than 7 million people who campaign for a world where human rights are enjoyed by all.</p><p>We are conducting a survey to gather your opinions and feedback on human rights issues and our work. The survey will take about 15 minutes to complete and your responses will be anonymous and confidential.</p><p>As a token of our appreciation, <mark data-explanation=\"2\">we will offer you a reward of $50</mark> if you complete the survey. To claim your reward, you will need to provide your email address at the end of the survey.</p><p>To start the survey, please open the attached file and follow the instructions.</p><p>Thank you for your participation and support.</p><p>Sincerely,<br>Amnesty International</p></div><span  data-explanation=\'3\'  data-position=1 id=\'component-attachment-2\'>Amnesty International Survey.pdf</span></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:05:55','2023-08-02 01:05:55'),(46,72,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Human Rights Watch</span><span  data-explanation=\'1\'  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>hrw@fellowship-tqwf.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Human Rights Watch Fellowship Opportunity</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear {{name}},</p><p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been selected as a potential candidate for the Human Rights Watch Fellowship Program. This is a prestigious opportunity for young professionals who are passionate about human rights and want to make a difference in the world.</p><p>The Human Rights Watch Fellowship Program is a one-year program that provides training, mentoring, and exposure to human rights work at the global level. Fellows work with our researchers, advocates, and lawyers on various projects and campaigns related to human rights issues in different regions and countries.</p><p>As a fellow, <mark data-explanation=\"2\">you will receive a monthly stipend of $2,000, health insurance, travel expenses</mark>, and access to our network of human rights experts and partners. You will also have the chance to participate in our annual Human Rights Watch Film Festival and other events.</p><p>To apply for the fellowship, you need to fill out an online application form and submit your resume, cover letter, and two references. The deadline for applications is February 15, 2021.</p><p>To access the application form, please click on the link below:</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://humanrights.watch.fellowship.com/application/form\"><mark data-explanation=\"3\">Human Rights Watch Fellowship Application Form</mark></a></p><p>Please note that this is a competitive program and only a limited number of candidates will be accepted. We encourage you to apply as soon as possible and to share this opportunity with your colleagues and friends who might be interested.</p><p>We look forward to receiving your application and working with you in the future.</p><p>Sincerely,</p><p>Kenneth Roth<br>Executive Director<br>Human Rights Watch</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:09:05','2023-08-02 01:09:05'),(47,73,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Nuri Shatta</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>shattan@hrf.org</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Job posting - Technology and human rights project manager at HRF</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Dear all,</p><p>Human Rights Forward is hiring a project manager for our new Technology and Human Rights division (see&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://jobs.humanrightsforward.org/tech-manager\">announcement</a>). The location is flexible. As you’ll see, the job description covers quite a lot. We’re encouraging people to apply even if you don’t think you meet all the qualifications, particularly if you are from backgrounds underrepresented in the NGO or tech sectors.</p><p>Please don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions. We’d also be most grateful if you could still share this opportunity far and wide.</p><p>All the best,<br>Nuri</p><p></p><p>Nuri Shatta,<br>Associate Manager, Technology<br>Human Rights Forward</p><p>PGP: 7D8F-2A3C-9B1E-4F6A-5B7D-8C9A-0E1F-3D2C-6B5E-4A3F</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://pronoun.is/she\">Pronoun.is/she</a></p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:12:40','2023-08-02 01:12:40'),(48,74,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-sender-name\'>Ava Wong</span><span  id=\'component-required-sender-email\'>ava.wong89@gmail.com</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'><span  id=\'component-optional-subject\'>Police violence on Market Street</span></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hi,</p><p>I\'m writing to report something I saw today. I was walking down Market Street in San Francisco yesterday at around noon when I saw a group of police officers arresting a guy. The guy was on the ground and handcuffed, and the cops were spraying him with pepper spray and hitting him with their batons.</p><p>It was really awful. The guy wasn\'t resisting arrest or anything, and he didn\'t look like he was a threat to the cops. I think the cops were using way too much force.</p><p>I know you guys are an organization that fights for human rights, so I thought you might want to know about this. I\'m not sure if you can do anything about it, but I thought it was worth a try.</p><p>Thanks for your time,</p><p>Ava</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:13:57','2023-08-02 01:13:57'),(49,75,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+249 91 234 5678</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Whatsapp</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Your WhatsApp account <mark data-explanation=\"1\">has been suspended</mark>. To verify your phone number and restore your WhatsApp account, click on this link: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://whatsapp-restore.com/we34gx\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">https://whatsapp-restore.com/we34gx</mark></a></p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:15:16','2023-08-02 01:15:16'),(50,76,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+880 1912 345678</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Human Rights Pioneers</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hello, this is Human Rights Pioneers. We are inviting you to join our group chat on Telegram to discuss the latest developments and challenges in human rights around the world. This is a secure and confidential platform where you can share your opinions and experiences with other human rights defenders and experts. To join the group chat, please click on this link:&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://www.telegramgroup-join.com/human-rights\"><mark data-explanation=\"1\">https://www.telegramgroup-join.com/human-rights</mark></a></p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:16:23','2023-08-02 01:16:23'),(51,77,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+261 71 25 93 84</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Alakay Rakoto</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hey {{name}}, I heard your organization is launching a new human rights program. If you have some time, I\'d love to chat to hear more about it and see if there are opportunities to collaborate. Let me know what you think!</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 01:17:30','2023-08-02 01:17:30'),(52,78,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+1(512) 555-1614</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Lila Mae Carter</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p><mark data-explanation=\"1\">Hello</mark>, I\'m a science writer for Scientific American and I\'m working on a feature article about the impact of social media on student mental health. I\'m hoping to interview some academics who have expertise in this area about this recent study on the impact of social media on student mental health: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://a0f9-2a02-8084.ngrok.io\"><mark data-explanation=\"2\">https://a0f9-2a02-8084.ngrok.io</mark></a>. Can you take a look and let me know if you have any thoughts on the findings?</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 13:05:06','2023-08-02 13:05:06'),(53,80,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+49 30 497369</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Lena Müller</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>I was going through some old photos the other day and I came across one of us from: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://icloud.com/photos/lenamuller294/My%20Vacation.jpg\">https://icloud.com/photos/lenamuller294/My%20Vacation.jpg</a>. It made me smile and I thought of you. How have you been? I\'d love to catch up sometime soon.</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 13:23:41','2023-08-02 13:23:41'),(54,81,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+48 72 319 44 90</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Tomasz Zielinski</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text-1\'><p>Hey, I’m new to the area and looking for some friends. Do you know any good places to hang out?</p></div></div></div>','2023-08-02 13:26:22','2023-08-02 13:26:22'),(55,82,1,'<div><div id=\'required-content\'><span  id=\'component-required-phone\'>+45 573310393</span><span  id=\'component-required-fullname\'>Hessa Al Qasimi</span></div><div id=\'optional-content\'></div><div id=\'dynamic-content\'><div data-position=\'0\' id=\'component-text